Wangcun Village in Jingde County in east China's Anhui Province is welcoming the blooming season for rapeseed flowers. Over 23 hectares of the bright-yellow flowers are blooming in terraced fields, attracting many visitors from all over the country. (Cover image is a screenshot. Video provided by Jiang Jianxing.) (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)